videos.headline: Patmon sheds defender to score 22-yard Cougars TD
videos.description: Anthony Gordon completes a pass to Dezmon Patmon who sheds his defender and treks into the end zone to score a 22-yard Washington State touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Patmon sheds defender to score 22-yard Cougars TD) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Montez throws 2 picks in the 1st half vs. Washington State
videos.description: Colorado's Steven Montez throws two interceptions in the first half against Washington State contributing to a 24-3 halftime deficit.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Montez throws 2 picks in the 1st half vs. Washington State) 2019/10/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Arconado scores 44-yard Cougars TD
videos.description: Anthony Gordon hits Brandon Arconado in stride as he goes into the end zone for a 44-yard Washington State touchdown.
